Jennifer Kent https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jennifer_Kent 0 Jennifer Kent is an Australian actress, writer and director, best known for her directorial debut, the horror film The Babadook (2014). Her second film, The Nightingale (2018), premiered at the 75th Venice International Film Festival.
